=Status=

" Sitra, we are strengthening our activities related to Fair Data Economy. Fair Data Economy will become a new strategic theme covering multiple projects for the next 4 years. This will give us more resources and continuum from our current project to focus on data economics in the future. Starting from 2021 there will be three main themes in Sitra: 1) Carbon-neutral circular economy, 2) Democracy and 3) Fair Data Economy."

(email, March 2021)

